  "description": "The shapeshifter and trickster who dwells among the gods despite being a giant's son. Blood-brother to <a class=\"corpus-link\" data-term=\"Odin\" data-tradition=\"norse\" href=\"../corpus-search.html?tradition=norse&amp;term=odin\" title=\"Search corpus for 'Odin'\">Odin</a>, <a class=\"corpus-link\" data-term=\"Father of Monsters\" data-tradition=\"norse\" href=\"../corpus-search.html?tradition=norse&amp;term=loki\" title=\"Search corpus for 'Father of Monsters'\">father of monsters</a>, helper and betrayer of the Aesir. His cunning brings both salvation and doom to the gods, culminating in the death of <a class=\"corpus-link\" data-term=\"Baldr\" data-tradition=\"norse\" href=\"../corpus-search.html?tradition=norse&amp;term=baldur\" title=\"Search corpus for 'Baldr'\">Baldr</a> and his binding until <a class=\"corpus-link\" data-term=\"Ragnarok\" data-tradition=\"norse\" href=\"../corpus-search.html?tradition=norse&amp;term=ragnarok\" title=\"Search corpus for 'Ragnarok'\">Ragnarok</a>.",
